SplitCodeBoard Licensing Notice
===============================

Copyright (c) 2026 SplitCodeBoard contributors.

This project is intentionally split-licensed by artifact type.

1) Firmware: AGPL-3.0-only
---------------------------

Scope:
- Firmware source code and firmware configuration, including content under:
  - zmk-config/
- Build/config files used to produce firmware images from this repository.

License:
- GNU Affero General Public License, version 3 only
- SPDX identifier: AGPL-3.0-only
- Full text: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt

2) Hardware: CERN-OHL-S-2.0
----------------------------

Scope:
- Hardware design sources, including KiCad and mechanical design artifacts, such as:
  - *.kicad_sch
  - *.kicad_pcb
  - *.kicad_pro
  - *.kicad_prl
  - *.step
  - keyboard/
  - SplitCodeBoard-backups/

License:
- CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Strongly Reciprocal
- SPDX identifier: CERN-OHL-S-2.0
- Full text: https://ohwr.org/cern_ohl_s_v2.txt

3) Other repository files
-------------------------

Unless a file explicitly states otherwise, files that are part of firmware
operation or configuration follow AGPL-3.0-only; files that are part of
hardware design sources follow CERN-OHL-S-2.0.

If a file includes an SPDX license identifier header, that header controls for
that file.
